        <h1>[FEATURED NEWS] HTXplains: What is artificial intelligence?</h1>
            <span class="description">
                Find out how AI works and what this technology could bring to our lives and the field of public safety
            </span>
            </div>
</div>
<div class="detail__content">
    <div class="container">
        <div id="Content_T472411FD001_Col01" class="sf_colsIn" data-placeholder-label="Social Sharing Widget"><section class="resizer-share article">
        <div class="date-author">
                <span class="date">Published on 03 September 2024</span>
                    </div>
    <div class="wrapper">
